%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Talk_Stage08_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 733d26e9e98269d4fb8f528880f9ce9e, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 189563105280
    m_Localized: I learned something recently.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105281
    m_Localized: Apparently, there is a section somewhere that has something called
      seasons.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105282
    m_Localized: There is a time when white fluff falls from above.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105283
    m_Localized: They say it feels cold when you touch it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105284
    m_Localized: And then, apparently,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105285
    m_Localized: there comes a time when white petals drift through the air.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105286
    m_Localized: Those short, fleeting dreams people have in that season...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105287
    m_Localized: I hear they call them spring dreams.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105288
    m_Localized: Spring dreams?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105289
    m_Localized: I might have seen something like that before I came here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105290
    m_Localized: There were red leaves falling everywhere.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189563105291
    m_Localized: Outside.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299584
    m_Localized: Outside.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299585
    m_Localized: '?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299586
    m_Localized: Sigh.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299587
    m_Localized: I told you before,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299588
    m_Localized: try not to say that word too much.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299589
    m_Localized: But if you have actually seen it,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299590
    m_Localized: then seasons really must exist!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299591
    m_Localized: Why aren't we supposed to talk about outside?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299592
    m_Localized: So what do you actually research?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299593
    m_Localized: I suppose it is a bit like being spirited away.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299594
    m_Localized: But I am still a scientist, technically.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299595
    m_Localized: I do not believe in spirits snatching people away. Or in gods, for
      that matter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299596
    m_Localized: You know the Paradise section, the place where the food appears?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299597
    m_Localized: There is a huge opening overhead, right?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299598
    m_Localized: I heard there might be a god beyond it,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299599
    m_Localized: so I decided to go and see for myself.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299600
    m_Localized: Could you see outside?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299601
    m_Localized: Not a chance.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299602
    m_Localized: There was glass in the way,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299603
    m_Localized: so I could not get out.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299604
    m_Localized: Some kinds of glass do not show what is on the other side,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299605
    m_Localized: and some look like paintings that move.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299606
    m_Localized: I imagine it was something like that.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299607
    m_Localized: I study patterns. Regularities in how this place behaves.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299608
    m_Localized: How often the food appears in Paradise.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299609
    m_Localized: How many beats it takes for a bomb to return after it disappears.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299610
    m_Localized: That sounds kind of boring.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189567299611
    m_Localized: What is any of that useful for?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493888
    m_Localized: The boring things are often the most useful, actually.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493889
    m_Localized: For example, if you know when the food will appear,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493890
    m_Localized: you can decide when to line up.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493891
    m_Localized: If you know when a bomb will come back,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493892
    m_Localized: you can decide when not to go near it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493893
    m_Localized: Incidentally, the supply timing is fixed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493894
    m_Localized: It happens right around when we start getting hungry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493895
    m_Localized: Huh. Convenient.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493896
    m_Localized: Do you choose what you research yourself?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493897
    m_Localized: Most of the time, the topics are assigned from higher up.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493898
    m_Localized: There are those who decide what should be investigated.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493899
    m_Localized: There are those who investigate it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493900
    m_Localized: And there are those who use the results.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493901
    m_Localized: I am the one in the middle.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493902
    m_Localized: I look into things no one else knows,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493903
    m_Localized: and eventually, someone is grateful for it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493904
    m_Localized: That makes me feel like I am alive. That is why I enjoy it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493905
    m_Localized: You talk too much...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493906
    m_Localized: But enjoying it is a good thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493907
    m_Localized: By the way, listening to you talk,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493908
    m_Localized: I keep feeling that something does not quite add up.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493909
    m_Localized: It sounds as if there was somewhere you were before coming here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493910
    m_Localized: If that is true, then your very existence
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493911
    m_Localized: would prove that outside exists, would it not?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493912
    m_Localized: Which means... wait, in other words...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493913
    m_Localized: Are you... a god?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493914
    m_Localized: Yes. And you have been speaking awfully casually to me this whole
      time!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493915
    m_Localized: Not even close. I am nothing that impressive.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493916
    m_Localized: No way! A mouse was a god this whole time!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493917
    m_Localized: Ahaha! This should do wonders for mousekind's reputation!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493918
    m_Localized: Hmph. Bow before me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493919
    m_Localized: But if a god came down to earth
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493920
    m_Localized: and cannot get back to heaven,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493921
    m_Localized: does that not make him basically the same as the rest of us?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493922
    m_Localized: Excuse me?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493923
    m_Localized: Besides, a god with a belly like that
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493924
    m_Localized: feels a little... fallen.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493925
    m_Localized: I am a god, you know. I am at the top.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493926
    m_Localized: That is what they call going out in disgrace.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493927
    m_Localized: (Grrr...)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493928
    m_Localized: Even so, you are a being from an unknown world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493929
    m_Localized: What, does that excite you because you are a scientist?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493930
    m_Localized: Or are you going to catch me and run experiments on me?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493931
    m_Localized: I told you before!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493932
    m_Localized: Harming others is against the rules.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493933
    m_Localized: Our peace is protected under the law.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493934
    m_Localized: But you do want to study me?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493935
    m_Localized: Slurp.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493936
    m_Localized: ?! That is the wrong kind of interested!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493937
    m_Localized: Chomp.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189571493938
    m_Localized: Ah!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688192
    m_Localized: Ahaha, I only said it out loud! I would not actually do it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688193
    m_Localized: (Taking this guy outside would be dangerous.)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688194
    m_Localized: Fwaaah... sigh. I am no good.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688195
    m_Localized: Lately it has been one experiment after another, almost no sleep.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688196
    m_Localized: Even I am getting sleepy.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688197
    m_Localized: There it is. The classic nerd flex.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688198
    m_Localized: '"I HAVEN''T SLEPT, I''M SO BUSY."'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688199
    m_Localized: You know, sometimes your personality is a real liability.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688200
    m_Localized: (Did I make him mad?)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688201
    m_Localized: Well, never mind. The reason I work myself this hard
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688202
    m_Localized: is that there is almost no such thing as entertainment in this world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688203
    m_Localized: People may look down on it,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688204
    m_Localized: but someone doing what Vanilla does
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688205
    m_Localized: is actually very important, I think.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688206
    m_Localized: She adds color to days that would otherwise be completely bland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688207
    m_Localized: How should I put it...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688208
    m_Localized: It is the sort of work only she can do, maybe.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688209
    m_Localized: What you do
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688210
    m_Localized: makes life better for a lot of people too.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688211
    m_Localized: Well... yes. Yes, that is true.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688212
    m_Localized: You say surprisingly decent things sometimes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688213
    m_Localized: Heh heh.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688214
    m_Localized: It is dark around here, so be careful.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688215
    m_Localized: Use a torch and you will be able to see a little farther in dark
      spaces.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 189575688216
    m_Localized: Make good use of it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
